---
title: Smoky Beef Tacos with Sautéed Peppers and Guacamole
description: We're giving your taco night an upgrade! Say goodbye to jarred salsa! Tonight's tacos are full of Mexican seasoned beef and creamy guacamole. Crunchy green onions and a squeeze of lime finish each taco with a fresh touch.
